{
    "version": "1.1.0",
    "description": "CyberChef-server - 通过 HTTP API 提供 CyberChef 数据处理功能的服务器",
    "homepage": "https://github.com/gchq/CyberChef-server",
    "license": "Apache-2.0",
    "url": "https://github.com/gchq/CyberChef-server/archive/refs/tags/v1.1.0.zip",
    "hash": "sha256:baa4cf78438706ecf7716f650df2da6b47d4e64bd29ca0f541be68c6805da5fb",
    "extract_dir": "CyberChef-server-1.1.0",
    "suggest": {
        "nodejs": "main/nodejs"
    },
    "pre_install": [
        "Push-Location \"$dir\"; npm.cmd install; Pop-Location",
        "Set-Content \"$dir\\cyberchef-server.bat\" '@pushd %~dp0', '@call node --experimental-json-modules index.mjs', '@popd' -Encoding Ascii"
    ],
    "bin": "cyberchef-server.bat",
    "checkver": "github",
    "autoupdate": {
        "url": "https://github.com/gchq/CyberChef-server/archive/refs/tags/v$version.zip",
        "extract_dir": "CyberChef-server-$version"
    },
    "notes": [
        "【工具类型】: 后端服务",
        "【主要功能】: 通过 REST API 提供 CyberChef 的数据编码、解码、加密、解密等功能",
        "【适用场景】: 需要程序化调用 CyberChef 功能的场景，支持多种编程语言通过 HTTP 请求调用",
        "【技术特点】: 基于 Node.js，提供 /bake 和 /magic 两个 API 端点",
        "【注意事项】: 运行前请确保已安装 Node.js，启动后访问 http://localhost:3000 查看 API 文档"
    ]
}
